    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>tomatoes</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>roughly and add to a bowl with the<strong> </strong>juice of half your <strong>lime</strong></p><p>Season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>, add a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>zingy salsa</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1596551895583-x200.jpg",
