          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) with your <strong>mayo</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>cold</strong> <strong>water</strong> in a bowl – this is your <strong>chipotle mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1596551902570-x200.jpg",
